Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:13.01,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,24 Hours\Nwith Asamori-san\NToday's\Nrelease!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.52,0:00:19.02,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,I'll buy you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.02,0:00:20.98,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,Rokuhara's\Nfirst work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:21.85,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,24 Hours\NThe Taiga Betrayal\Nwith Asamori-san\NRecommended\NReleased\NGames\NToday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:22.73,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,The Taiga Betrayal\NRecommended\NGames
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:23.94,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,24 Hours\NThe Taiga Betrayal\Nwith Asamori-san\NRecommended\NReleased\NGames\NToday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls Beyond\Nthe Wasteland
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.70,0:00:45.12,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Zetsubou to kakki wa hitoe\NDespair and energy are one and the same
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.12,0:00:47.83,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Jinsei wa hakanakute\NLife is short
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.84,0:00:49.25,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Kusubutte irarenai\NWe can't stay like this forever
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.26,0:00:52.67,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Dakara arukidasou\NSo let's start walking forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.17,0:00:57.34,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Yukedo hatenai kono michi o\NWhat are you moving towards
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:02.26,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Nani o hoshite susundeiku\NOn this endless road?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.02,0:01:07.68,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Mizu o motome samayou you ni\NYou won't get anywhere with hope without desire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:13.73,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Yoku no nai kibou ni mirai wa nai\NAs if you're wandering looking only for water
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:18.15,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Monogatari no algorithm\NThe pilgrims pursue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.95,0:01:23.74,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Tadoru junreishatachi\NThe algorithm of the story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.04,0:01:28.16,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Mune ni yadoru sono shin'nen ga\NThe faith in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:32.79,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Death march wo ikinokoru sube\NHelps us survive this death march
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.17,0:01:35.71,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Imagination no flow\NThe imagination flows!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.71,0:01:40.38,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Junsui no mama ja iranai kanaetai dattara\NYou can't stay pure if you want your dream to come true
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:45.10,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Furenai unmei wo egakidasou\NLet's create an impossible fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:48.18,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Tada matteitatte tsumannai\NIt's boring just waiting around
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.18,0:01:50.44,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Sou kanjiteitan janai\NThat's how you felt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:55.02,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Yume wa jibun de ubaitsukamu diamond\NYour dreams are a diamond you have to take for yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:58.07,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Chousen no turn\NIt's our turn for challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:02:00.70,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Jounetsu no zone\NThe passionate zone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.82,0:02:03.32,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Tomo ni tatte\NLet's stand together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:06.45,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Fumidashite mezasu kouya wo\NTake our first steps as we aim for the wasteland
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"Beyond."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,At or on the further side of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have learned that word in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Combine that with the English word "youth"\Nfor the phrase "beyond youth".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the age of youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:03:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You are all in the midst of your age of youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But what lies beyond that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you thought about what lies beyond youth?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Um!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you guys go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you say it, Bunta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's fine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.21,0:03:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I remember, Nakajima made\Nthat awesome flip today in gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right. That was crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he made the landing\Non that triple twist flip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That deserved a gold medal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, there's not enough consistency!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! There is too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A consistency called love!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All that needs to be consistent are their lower halves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I'm so done with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, you heading up to the club room, too, Ando-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A-are you all going to the club room?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it alright if I join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I mean, we're going to the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Um! Today's really our release date, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It just hasn't fully hit me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Tori-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't felt it yet, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:05:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so everyone's feeling the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm like "oh man, it's really on sale?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing? Open it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you nervous, Bunta?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,S-shut up! I am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuroda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-wha--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! Hurry up and come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, that just now, was it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as I predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a repeat order.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All 3,000 of our initial units sold in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The shops are making additional orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I just finished up with ZEGA, they discussed\Na proposal for more production.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How much more do they want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Twice our initial order.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Twice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That many?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they'd all sell right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, combining that with the other numbers...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,T-that's... nine thousand...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And looking at Typhoon's sales...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They sold out of all 4,000 of their initial order as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They had more straight from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,S-so we lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, their repeat order is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a repeat order of 6,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Theirs is only 2,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations. We've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Atomu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it, Bunta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,9,000 versus 6,000, isn't that kinda crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:06:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we're geniuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Asamori-san is a low-priced game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Taiga", on the other hand, is a full-priced game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The price difference may have\Ninfluenced the difference in sales.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So we had the advantage from the start,\Njust 'cause we went with sale numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know if we would win until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a direct result from our genuine hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuroda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,To celebrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a cake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, you prepped well for this, Kuroda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuroda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:39.39,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,Yakiniku\NKaifutei
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:41.31,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,Yakiniku Kaifutei
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That hits the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,After working hard, you've gotta\Ndrink a cold one of these!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cola... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.86,0:08:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Bunta, cook up some meat! Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna have some skirt steak. The top cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The top?! Can we really order that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's do the special cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's even more expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to eat, Atomu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have the beef tongue, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the salted beef tongue good?\NHow about you, Yuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,One order of kalbi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's get the special cut of all of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the special cut is too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get the special cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way tougher than the top cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seriously heavy cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,T-then I'll have the special green onion-stuffed cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Torry's way less hesitant than she used to be, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Y-you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At first you'd be like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"I-I think everything is fine like this..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Whaa?\NYeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Whaa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I think she was always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shyness and a lack thereof can coexist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can have your cake and eat it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, it's good that you're more honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You take that to the extreme, though, Yuka.\NJust be yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You take that to the extreme, though, Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But man, there aren't many teams out there\Nthat make it to the end
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,with everyone being honest\Nand saying how they feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,For once, we agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I was cooking that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the rules of the wasteland.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you didn't want me to take it,\Nyou should've written your name on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, it's all cooked, so let's eat, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, we'd like to put in an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, one skirt steak, kalbi, beef tongue,\Nand a green onion stuffed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All special cuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:10:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuroda's brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? I work here part time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,At a yakiniku restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The hourly pay's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about your debt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The money you're making will\Ngo into your next work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to all of you, I've started moving again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all in the past for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right, hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully this makes up for it a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want meat! Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like something sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just work part-time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, you could have it if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You seem like a nice guy\Nwho'd eat this kinda stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A "nice guy?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap, he's reopening Atomu's old wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, uh, I'll eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I love veggies, they're so yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she loved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she loved nice guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry my brother was so rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my kalbi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really juicy 'n warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Normies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn 'em all! No, cook 'em!\NCook all the normies alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Cook up that meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Atomu, eat, eat! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I ate a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see meat for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I ate so much meat, there's no way\Nthey can call a vegetarian beta, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuroda-san? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This ice cream is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I want some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuroda-san, want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dual-wielding!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The life of luxury.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you're not cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 'cause it's daring!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still surprised we actually won.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't think we'd win?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.15,0:13:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it was more dangerous for us\Nin the long run than just on the day of release.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Asamori-san was written in an easygoing,\Neveryday setting, so people are quick to pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand,\N"Taiga" is a game with a lot of depth,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,so it will continue to sell\Nhundreds of units every month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There may not be many people talking about\NAsamori-san a year from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But "Taiga" might end up being a work that\Npeople are talking about many years down the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta work harder, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just the beginning for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, there was something\NI wanted to ask you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking of dissolving Rokuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dissolving?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? What happened to making two games?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! You said we would!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that working together with people\Nand making something could be so fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:15:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I should have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was so much more fun than I'd thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.89,0:15:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want to put an end to\Neverything the past me has done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to start over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make a game from square one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we make a game\Npurely for ourselves this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Purely for ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.87,0:15:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It means exactly what it sounds like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of worrying about what will and won't sell,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,let's make something we really\Nwant to make and enjoy making it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.09,0:15:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone puts in their input\Nand decides on a project.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.39,0:15:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The deadline will be flexible,\Nand we can really think the quality through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, this time I'll make sure\Nyou're properly compensated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to make a game with me once more?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to do it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hojo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't make a game with you in\Nsuch a lukewarm manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\NI feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get why we have to pretend to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I've debuted,\Nmy second work is pretty important!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I like having fun, but I dunno if I\Ncan handle no schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought professionals did their best\Nwithin their time limit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But is that what you all want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This world is a wasteland, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you can't survive just doing what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the ones with passion burning in their hearts\Ncan grasp their dreams in this cruel wasteland!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you teach me that, Kuroda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.09,0:17:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll definitely win next time, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.14,0:17:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hells yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.48,0:17:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all work hard together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! So let's do a BL game th--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why? You meanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:34.16,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,Mitsuteru-san\NCalling
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Buntarou, did you hear the numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We won, I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,About that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Taiko-san's already started complaining about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you freakin' kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She's making a big fuss about having to\Nbow down to high schoolers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it'd be alright if I was the only one who--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:18:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm really looking forward to\NTaiko-san bowing down to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.07,0:18:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more of a sadist than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Kuroda.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,About picking someone to join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you never ask that of us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Then you owe us one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Making people owe you is the best feeling ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well, that's what my boss says,\Nso I guess that settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But all things aside, if you look at\Nthe script itself, I win, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We won by units!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I read a bunch of reviews,\Nand mine had much higher ratings!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We still won our competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won the game, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what you're talking about, Ohgi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm the one who doesn't understand you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was a ridiculous ending to our battle.\NNo, I'm the one who doesn't understand you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was a ridiculous ending to our battle.\NNo, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was a ridiculous ending to our battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:55.58,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,PC game sales rankings
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A few days later, I checked the\Nsales rankings on a big online store.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But the results were...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:03.46,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,ChuChu.com\NWhat are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.38,0:19:05.63,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,Games
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:08.17,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,1st      Wear LOVE: It feels best when you're wearing me!\N2nd      24 Hours with Asamori-san\N3rd      The Taiga Betrayal
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"1st: Wear LOVE: It feels best when you're wearing me?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of game is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sexy battle game where the main character\Ngets turned into a suit of armor by a curse
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and protects the heroine while also fighting evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That was written and produced by Hosokawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear it sold 20,000 copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's hard to find in stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:36.87,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,Computing Weekly
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.32,0:19:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The game writer Hosokawa is huge in the media.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:39.16,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,All about Hosokawa
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,His game quickly got an anime adaptation,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course a manga and\Nnovel adaptation, and also a movie,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:41.33,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Games are like parfaits!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and an idol group was born from the project.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:47.76,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,Another big project from\Nproducer and writer\NBlooters!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The world had a Hosokawa Fever like no other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:50.93,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,Signing Event
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...Or so I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hosokawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:19:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:19:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Heyo, Hojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are kinda crazy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,For various reason,\NI'm gonna have to fade away for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry if it causes trouble for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Buh-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.07,0:20:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Kawakoshishi Productions.\NYes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Kawakoshishi Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Hosokawa-san there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Kawakado Editing department,\Nis Hosokawa-san--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Hosokawa-san--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Hosokawa-san--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hosokawa-san--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.09,0:20:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hosokawa-san got a bit uppity and took on\Ntoo many projects, then suddenly deflated,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Hosokawa Fever met its demise\Nas quickly as it'd begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary...\Nand the Hosokawa Fever met its demise\Nas quickly as it'd begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Hosokawa Fever met its demise\Nas quickly as it'd begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,As for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.86,0:20:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:50.99,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,Graduation Plans
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.82,0:20:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who hasn't turned it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.82,0:20:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hojo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuroda-san, I thought you'd already\Ngone up to the club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:20:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was talking with our teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.58,0:21:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's head up together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it! You can't leave until you finish this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was serious about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm gonna check it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.51,0:21:15.89,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,Employment Plans\NI'm still looking for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.76,0:21:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's Hosokawa-san going to do from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he's going to work for anyone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.06,0:21:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to restore your name to what it was\Nonce it's gone down is really difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the wasteland for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.06,0:21:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But suddenly returning and working as if\Nnothing happened is also part of the wasteland.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.03,0:21:36.45,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,Getting inspiration!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll continue on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.96,0:21:46.33,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,Yuka\NCome up to the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Marching forth in this land where there's\Nno place for lip service.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what'll make us keep on...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Or what's waiting for us in the distance...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.77,0:22:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But no matter how reckless...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.65,0:22:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we don't know when it'll fall apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.86,0:22:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what little seams we tear apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.49,0:22:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.56,0:22:32.03,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Atarashii sekai tobikome mirai ga yonderu\NJump into the new world, our future is calling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.03,0:22:35.03,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Yasashiku yorisottettai\NI want to gently be by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.03,0:22:38.57,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Kimi no yume ouensasete\NLet me support you and your dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:54.01,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Chotto jiman dekiru mono\NSomeone who doesn't have
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.09,0:22:57.05,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Nan ni mo motteinakute\NAnything they can be proud of
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.05,0:23:00.47,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Ki ga tsuitara shita bakari\NOn cloudy days when they realize
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.47,0:23:03.47,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Mitsumeteta no cloudy days\NThey've only been looking at the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.68,0:23:06.69,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Sonna uyamuya shiteiru\NI want to change
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.69,0:23:09.61,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Futoumei na kimochi wa ne\NThat wavering, murky feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.61,0:23:13.61,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Jibun datte ni kaete hoshii\NInto a shout of "I can do it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.40,0:23:17.15,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Hajimete zukushi de\NWhen I'm first starting out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.15,0:23:20.11,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Tomadoi darake dakedo\NI'm full of so many doubts
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.12,0:23:22.87,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Watashi mo onaji da yo\NIt's the same for me, too
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.08,0:23:29.96,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Atarashii sekai tobikome mirai ga matteru\NJump into the new world, our future is waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.96,0:23:35.55,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Hikari ni mitasareta toki motomete\NPursue a moment full of light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.55,0:23:42.05,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Gamushara ni ikeru shunkan sono saki ima da yo\NThe present awaits us after this frantic moment
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.39,0:23:45.14,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Yasashiku yorisottettai\NI want to gently be by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.14,0:23:48.81,Def_Ita,,0,0,0,,Dakara issho ni ganbarou\NSo let's all work hard together
